<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Cancellation Notification</title>
    <style>
      body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f9f9f9; margin:
      0; padding: 0; color: #333; } .email-container { max-width: 600px; margin:
      40px auto; background-color: #ffffff; border: 1px solid #eee; border-left:
      4px solid #e27a82; border-radius: 8px; padding: 24px; } .header {
      text-align: center; margin-bottom: 20px; } .header img { max-height: 40px;
      display: block; margin: 0 auto 10px; } .fallback-logo { color: #e27a82;
      font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; } .title { font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: bold; color: #e27a82; text-align: center; margin-bottom:
      20px; } .email-body { font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; } ol {
      padding-left: 18px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; } .email-body
      ol li { margin-bottom: 10px; } .button-link { display: block; width:
      fit-content; margin: 20px auto; background-color: #e27a82 !important;
      color: #ffffff !important; padding: 12px 24px; border-radius: 6px;
      text-decoration: none !important; text-align: center; font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: bold; } .button-link:hover { background-color: #c86a67
      !important; color: #ffffff !important; } .footer { font-size: 13px; color:
      #777; text-align: center; margin-top: 40px; border-top: 1px solid #eee;
      padding-top: 16px; } a:not(.button-link) { color: #0066cc;
      text-decoration: underline; word-break: break-word; }
      a:not(.button-link):hover { text-decoration: underline; color: #0056b3; }
      .success-box { background-color: #d4edda; border-left: 4px solid #28a745;
      padding: 15px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="email-container">
      <!-- Logo with fallback -->
      <div class="header">
        <div style="height: 40px; margin-bottom: 10px; text-align: center">
          <a
            href="{{frontend_url}}"
            target="_blank"
            style="display: inline-block"
          >
            <img
              src="{{frontend_url}}/logo.png"
              alt="Fatima's Therapy Services"
              width="100"
              height="100"
              style="max-height: 100%; display: block; margin: 0 auto"
              onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.parentElement.innerHTML='<div style=\'color:#E27A82;font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;\'>Fatima's Therapy Services</div>';"
            />
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Title -->
      <div class="title">Cancellation Notification</div>

      <!-- Message Body -->
      <div class="email-body">
        <p>Dear Admin,</p>

        <div class="success-box">
          <p><strong>âœ… Eligible for Refund:</strong>
            This cancellation was made within the
            {{cancelCutoffDays}}-day notice period and is eligible for a refund.</p>
        </div>

        <p>
          A session has been cancelled by
          {{name}}. Since this cancellation was made within the required notice
          period, the client is eligible for a refund. Here are the details:
        </p>

        <ol>
          <li><strong>User Email:</strong> {{userEmail}}</li>
          <li><strong>Booking ID:</strong> {{bookingId}}</li>
          <li>
            <strong>Event Date and Time:</strong>
            {{eventDate}}
            at
            {{eventTime}}
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Cancellation Date:</strong>
            {{cancellationDate}}
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Cancelled By:</strong>
            {{cancelledBy}}
          </li>
          <li><strong>Payment Amount:</strong>
            {{paymentAmount}}
            {{paymentCurrency}}</li>
          <li>
            <strong>Payment Status:</strong>
            {{paymentStatus}}
            {{#if paymentCompleted}}on {{paymentCompleted}}{{/if}}
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Transaction Reference Number:</strong>
            {{transactionReferenceNumber}}
          </li>
        </ol>

        <p>Please follow these steps to process the refund:</p>

        <ol>
          <li>Log in to your Safepay dashboard</li>
          <li>
            Find the transaction using the reference number above
          </li>
          <li>
            Process the refund through the Safepay interface
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Important:</strong>
            Verify the transaction details match before processing
          </li>
        </ol>

        <a href="{{refundLink}}" class="button-link">Process Refund</a>

        <p>If you have any questions, feel free to reach out.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Footer -->
      <div class="footer">
        Regards,<br />
        Fatima's Therapy Services<br />
        &copy;
        {{currentYear}}
        All rights reserved.
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>